    Plots several summaries of an ngvb.list object.

    plot.Rd

    Plots several summaries of an ngvb.list object.

    Usage

    # S4 method for ngvb.list,missing
plot(x, y, ...)

    Arguments

    x

    An ngvb.list object (output of ngvb function)

    y

    Not used.

    ...

    Extra arguments to be used in plot(x@LGM, ...) where x@LGM is an inla object.

    Examples

     #Here we fit an RW1 latent process to the jumpts time series
 plot(jumpts)


 #Fit LGM with INLA
 LGM     <- inla(y ~ -1 + f(x,  model = "rw1"),
                 data = jumpts)

 #Fit LnGM with ngvb
 LnGM <- ngvb(fit = LGM, selection = list(x=1:100))
